title: Adobe Camera RAW 9.0 Plug-in (Win + Mac)
description:
Camera RAW 9.0 is applicable for Photoshop CS6, Photoshop CC, Photoshop CC 2014.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW FEATURES

    Merge to HDR and Panorama

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PERFORMANCE IMPROVEMENTS

    Camera Raw can now use the Graphics Processing Unit (GPU) to speed up
    interactive image editing. The GPU is particularly helpful when using high
    resolution screens, such as 4K and 5K displays.

Minimum system requirements:

    64-bit only
    Mac OS 10.9 and higher or Windows 7 and higher

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW CAMERA SUPPORT IN CAMERA RAW 9

    Canon EOS 5DS
    Canon EOS 5DS R
    Canon EOS 750D (Rebel T6i, Kiss X8i)
    Canon EOS 760D (Rebel T6s, Kiss 8000D)
    Canon EOS M3
    Casio EX-ZR3500
    Fujifilm X-A2
    Fujifilm XQ2
    Hasselblad Stellar II
    Nikon D5500
    Nikon D7200
    Olympus OM-D E-M5 II
    Olympus Stylus SH-2
    Olympus Tough TG-4
    Panasonic Lumix DMC-GF7
    Panasonic Lumix DMC-ZS50 (DMC-TZ70, DMC-TZ71)
    Samsung NX500
